# Final check for connectivity:
# All Agents are linked to teams, and manage resources/applications/services.
# All Locations are linked hierarchically.
# All ProductModels are linked to manufacturers.
# All Resources are linked to ProductModels, Agents, Locations, and Applications.
# All NetworkInterfaces are linked to Resources and NetworkLinks.
# All NetworkLinks are linked to NetworkInterfaces and Resources.
# All Applications are linked to Agents and Resources.
# All ApplicationModules are linked to Applications and Agents.
# All Services are linked to ApplicationModules/Applications and Agents.
# All OperationPlans are linked to Pre/Post Conditions.
# All EventRecords are linked to Resources/Applications/Agents and TroubleTickets/ChangeRequests.
# All TroubleTickets are linked to Services/Applications/Resources, Agents, EventRecords, and Notes.
# All ChangeRequests are linked to Resources/Applications/Services, Agents, and EventRecords.
# All TroubleTicketNotes are linked to TroubleTickets and Agents.
# All DocumentAttachments are linked to TroubleTickets/ChangeRequests.
# AnomalyPatterns are linked to TroubleTickets.

# The graph is dense, connected, and uses only NORIA vocabulary and standard prefixes.
# The ldp prefix is not used.
